data.description: Welcome home to this charming home located in North Laredo, This stunning 2-story gem boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 2,358sqft of living space. With its modern design and thoughtful layout, this house is perfect for creating memories with loved ones. Don't miss out, make this dreamy abode yours.
